---
title: Diner-Style BLT Sandwiches with Parmesan-Ranch Tossed Salad
description: The fresh aroma after a spring rain, a starry night, a perfect peach: It’s the simple things that often bring the most joy, like a BLT! And this one’s a classic: toasted sourdough slathered with spicy seasoned mayo and layered with smoky bacon, juicy tomatoes, and crisp lettuce. Just like at the diner, we’ve got a side salad for you—a creamy, crunchy buttermilk ranch-dressed number, showered with Parmesan. It’s the perfect pairing for one of our favorite sandwiches of all time.
